# Rect (x,y,w,h) area + perimeter.
*mkrect(x as i64, y as i64, w as i64, h as i64) returns Vec of i64
    r is vec()
    r.push(x)
    r.push(y)
    r.push(w)
    r.push(h)
    r

*area(r as Vec of i64) returns i64
    r.get(2) * r.get(3)

*perim(r as Vec of i64) returns i64
    2 * (r.get(2) + r.get(3))

*main
    r is mkrect(0, 0, 5, 7)
    log area(r)
    log perim(r)
